{
  "text": "First, let us fix an integer J that specifies the window length of the low-pass filter. For the sake of simplicity, we consider G\u00e1bor filters [CITATION_1] . These filters provide a good localization tradeoff between frequency and space planes, due to Heisenberg uncertainty principle [CITATION_2] . Thus, having",
